text: Preen may refer to: == Birds == *Preen, personal grooming of a bird's feathers especially by using its beak *Preen gland, also called the uropygial gland, an oil gland found in many bird species *Preen oil, an oil made by the uropygial gland found in many bird species ==Products== *Preen, a trade name for trifluralin == Surname == *Garyn Preen (born 1991), Welsh footballer *Alan Preen (born 1935), former sportsman who played Australian rules football == Social arts & Attire == *Accessories *Foreplay *Fragrance *Hairstyle *Waxing
